      • SimpleCloudProviderMetadata

        public SimpleCloudProviderMetadata(String id,
                                   String name,
                                   String description,
                                   List<ConfigurationProperty> configurationProperties,
                                   CredentialsProviderMetadata credentialsProviderMetadata,
                                   List<ResourceProviderMetadata> resourceProviderMetadata)
        Creates an abstract cloud provider metadata with the specified parameters.
        Parameters:
        id - the unique identifier of the provider within its scope
        name - the name of the provider, suitable for display in a drop-down menu of peer providers within the same scope
        description - the human-readable description of the provider
        configurationProperties - the list of configuration properties that can be given to configure the provider
        credentialsProviderMetadata - the credentials provider metadata
        resourceProviderMetadata - the metadata about the supported resource providers
